  "url": "https://www.ada.lk/breaking_news/\u0dc3\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dc0-\u0db4\u0dcf\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dd2\u0d9a-\u0d85\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dbb-\u0d86\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0da7-\u0d89\u0da9-\u0daf\u0dd3\u0db8-\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dbd\u0dd4-\u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dda-\u0dc0\u0d9c\u0d9a\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dba\u0dd2/11-395289",
  "time_ut": 1657436568,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dc0 \u0db4\u0dcf\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dd2\u0d9a \u0d85\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dbb \u0d86\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0d89\u0da9 \u0daf\u0dd3\u0db8 \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dbd\u0dd4 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dda \u0dc0\u0d9c\u0d9a\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "It is everyone's responsibility to allow an all-party interim government",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Minister Prasanna Ranatunga said in a statement that it should be the responsibility of the people's representatives to allow the all-party interim government that the people are demanding.",
        "It is seen in the announcement issued by him that the country has faced a critical situation and all the rulers who have ruled this country for 74 years should be held responsible for the country getting into this situation.",
        "\"Today, our motherland is facing a critical moment in its history. All the rulers who ruled this country for seventy-four years are responsible for the motherland becoming in this tragic state. Inefficient governance is the main reason for the economic hardships these people are facing today.",
        "In order to fulfill the expectations of the people, the President, who was elected with a mandate of 69 lakhs, has been strongly influenced by the people to leave the office. The President has already announced that he will leave his office on the thirteenth of this month bowing to the people's opinion. Therefore, our responsibility as the people's representatives at this moment is not to give band-aids that the people no longer trust. Our responsibility is to provide quick solutions to the problems faced by the people at present as well as to provide the necessary space for appointing representatives that the people trust. It should happen according to the constitution. Taking the lead for that is an unavoidable duty and responsibility assigned to all 225 people's representatives in the Parliament.",
        "Therefore, our duty and responsibility at this moment is to give space to the all-party interim government that the people are asking for. To support the all-party interim government in providing solutions to all the problems like oil, gas, fertilizer, electricity, essential food that are oppressing the people at the moment.",
        "Setting up a system to provide medicines to the people without shortage. Taking necessary steps to properly maintain the education of children who have been affected by the covid epidemic and the current economic crisis. I believe that within a short period of time a specific program should be held to solve the problems faced by the people and give the people the opportunity to form the government they want."
      ],
